Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.06,0:05:42.97,title,NTP,0,0,0,,小羊们的休假{\fad(1300,0)}{\pos(512,419)}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:06.47,0:00:07.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.73,0:00:08.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:09.11,0:00:11.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说了不去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.93,0:00:17.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起这个来 你那种傻气的反应就不能改改吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:17.37,0:00:19.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是姐姐大人 那约好的事情怎么办?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:20.81,0:00:23.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没打算不遵守约定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:23.83,0:00:28.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但祐巳你老是这么迫不及待的情绪高昂…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:28.95,0:00:32.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我一直期待着啊 去游乐园玩…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.36,0:00:35.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是说不去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:36.20,0:00:40.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是在商量现在就去是否不太合适而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:40.76,0:00:45.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,骗人 姐姐大人刚才清清楚楚地说「不去」了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:45.69,0:00:47.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别挑语病了好吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.41,0:00:50.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最近真是喜欢和我唱反调呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:51.34,0:00:53.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是因为姐姐大人的一字一句
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:53.44,0:00:57.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都无情地刺痛胆小的我那脆弱的内心啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.42,0:01:01.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊? 这么能顶嘴 真是服了你这胆小鬼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.35,0:01:12.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 放着她们俩不管不太好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:15.39,0:01:19.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐妹间亲热的斗嘴 不识相地介入才不太好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:20.37,0:01:21.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是说不用阻止她们了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:22.25,0:01:24.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系~ 只不过是在闹着玩罢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:25.52,0:01:26.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闹着玩?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:33.39,0:01:34.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 要再来一杯对吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:37.35,0:01:38.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我这就去倒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:39.76,0:01:40.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是善解人意呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:42.50,0:01:44.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是身为妹妹的本分嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.11,0:01:52.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.40,0:01:55.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐妹吵嘴这种事情别说狗不理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.55,0:01:57.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就连细菌也不会去看一眼的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.90,0:02:05.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,游乐园这种地方 暑假里应该是人山人海的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.62,0:02:07.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.69,0:02:11.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且我比较怕热
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.63,0:02:14.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每年夏天都是到避暑的别墅去住的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.48,0:02:16.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,游乐园等到冬天再去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.67,0:02:18.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.60,0:02:22.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本来打算暑假和姐姐大人一起去玩的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.69,0:02:26.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,提议一个只适合夏天去游玩的地方就行了嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.57,0:02:28.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就是这么办的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.40,0:02:31.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由乃同学夏天打算去哪里玩?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.17,0:02:33.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呵~呵~呵~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.02,0:02:35.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呵呵呵?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.60,0:02:36.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,登富士山!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.74,0:02:37.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.99,0:02:40.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这可是我长久以来一直未了的心愿呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.35,0:02:42.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手术后也快满十个月了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.07,0:02:44.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且还获得了主治医生的许可
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.00,0:02:46.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再加上有某监护人一起同行~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.08,0:02:49.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由乃同学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.28,0:02:54.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又用了强硬手段勉强让医生和令大人点头了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.81,0:02:59.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,志摩子同学 暑假里有什么安排?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.80,0:03:01.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我打算和乃梨子一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.27,0:03:04.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,参观各地的教堂和佛像展
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.73,0:03:09.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真棒 果然适合你们这一对的风格呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.61,0:03:10.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么说祐巳同学的安排呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.17,0:03:15.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,照往年看的话 应该是到山梨县的奶奶家里去…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.88,0:03:16.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祐巳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.88,0:03:18.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 什么事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.82,0:03:19.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要来吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.88,0:03:20.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.41,0:03:26.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,方便的话 到我家的别墅来玩吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.85,0:03:29.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.92,0:03:31.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦~~~?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.56,0:03:37.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聚集在玛莉亚的庭院里的少女们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.58,0:03:42.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天也带着天使般无垢的笑容 穿过高大的校门
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.67,0:03:47.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,覆盖住纯洁身心的是深色的制服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.90,0:03:51.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不让裙子上的褶痕乱掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.08,0:03:54.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不让白色的水手领翻起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.72,0:03:58.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舒缓地行走成了这里的习俗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.14,0:04:01.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,私立莉莉安女学园
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.01,0:04:05.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是少女的花园
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.49,0:05:51.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还想邀请什么人一起来别墅玩吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.32,0:05:53.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.60,0:05:57.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,方便的话 可以多叫两三个人一起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.73,0:06:01.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐大人 除了我之外还邀请了其他人吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.43,0:06:03.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.76,0:06:04.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.13,0:06:07.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要不要邀请圣大人一起来?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.01,0:06:10.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和圣大人一起的话 祐巳应该会很开心吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.82,0:06:14.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是她们大学生不是有讨论会之类的要参加吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.38,0:06:17.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…也许是有呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.58,0:06:23.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐大人 只有我一人去的话觉得不够吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.79,0:06:26.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.89,0:06:29.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也真是的 怎么这么爱胡思乱想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.26,0:06:33.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的话 只要祐巳能来就十分满足了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.66,0:06:37.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是啊 只要能和姐姐大人一起的话…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.37,0:06:39.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有两个人不要紧吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.68,0:06:40.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.51,0:06:46.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使只有两个人 只要在一起就能够开心地度过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.37,0:06:50.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,此时的我 对这点还深信不疑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.65,0:06:56.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听见了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.10,0:06:58.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听见了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.15,0:07:03.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小笠原家的别墅 我也好想被邀请去看看呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.62,0:07:07.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行的话 至少能偷看一眼红蔷薇姐妹的休假也好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.39,0:07:11.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但那是私有土地 应该不能随便进入的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.26,0:07:16.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托祐巳同学带我们一起去如何?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.55,0:07:19.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说不定她会点头同意呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.89,0:07:24.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但在看了这副两人世界般的样子之后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.44,0:07:26.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,实在不好开口呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.36,0:07:27.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去了会当电灯泡的~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.99,0:07:29.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确实是所谓的电灯泡呢~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.23,0:07:32.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊~ 但是真的好想看啊~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.23,0:07:34.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真想看呢~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.66,0:07:39.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,红蔷薇大人和花蕾那优雅而又平静的假期生活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.18,0:07:48.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后 期待已久的暑假终于开始了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.46,0:07:51.22,day,NTP,0,0,0,,星期一{\fad(500,0)}{\pos(502,520)}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.40,0:07:57.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喔 把最宝贝的衣服拿出来啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.73,0:07:58.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很花心思嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.29,0:08:00.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.60,0:08:03.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是去别墅而已吧 放松一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.36,0:08:06.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,短暂的休假要好好享受喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.03,0:08:07.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.23,0:08:11.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我这周因为学生会的合宿也会到那附近去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.03,0:08:13.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那边也许能碰面呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.99,0:08:15.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.24,0:08:19.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这件连衣裙看着像纹白蝶呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.41,0:08:23.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪里有什么花纹啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.54,0:08:24.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这句话是在说俏皮话?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.54,0:08:24.55,reference,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs26}注:「紋（もん）なんかついてないもん」这句话开头和结尾都是念mon
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.17,0:08:25.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.10,0:08:35.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 没什么好紧张的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.27,0:08:37.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是去别墅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.78,0:08:41.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去那儿与姐姐大人共度愉快的一周而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.19,0:08:42.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祐巳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.11,0:08:43.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.78,0:08:46.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为…为什么是穿牛仔裤?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.13,0:08:50.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早安 祐巳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.02,0:08:52.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好可爱的连衣裙啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.35,0:08:56.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐大人才是 新牛仔裤真配
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.42,0:09:01.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 上次情人节祐巳帮我挑的那件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.61,0:09:03.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不时在家里穿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.56,0:09:05.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祖父他看到后就买了这件给我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.09,0:09:07.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好高档的样子…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.19,0:09:08.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 我们出发吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.64,0:09:09.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 姐姐大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.51,0:09:13.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剪票口的话在这边…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.04,0:09:16.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是说过坐车去的嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.73,0:09:18.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有啊 不记得听您这么说过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.64,0:09:22.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的确说了坐车去的呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.82,0:09:23.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「车」吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.14,0:09:25.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对 「车」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.01,0:09:27.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,车…车…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.65,0:09:29.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.85,0:09:30.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐大人的确说过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.07,0:09:32.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「如果提前到了约定地点的话」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.30,0:09:37.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「我会在你来之前先打发一下时间」这样的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.75,0:09:38.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对呀 说过的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.58,0:09:42.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果早到的话 就会在有冷气的车上…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.94,0:09:43.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.29,0:09:46.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「在车上」与「来之前」…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.29,0:09:51.39,reference,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs26}注:日语中「在车上  車で」与「来之前  来るまで」这两个词只有音调略有不同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.23,0:09:51.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 我们俩理解成不同的意思了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.87,0:10:00.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,味道如何?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.13,0:10:02.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很美味呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.44,0:10:03.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.07,0:10:05.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么再尝尝这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.72,0:10:08.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真羡慕祐巳呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.75,0:10:11.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我从没有带着妈妈做的便当
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.68,0:10:14.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去参加远足或运动会之类活动的经历呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.00,0:10:17.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,清子阿姨不做的吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.73,0:10:20.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然会做 但非常花时间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.10,0:10:23.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甚至有过我都从远足回来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.33,0:10:25.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,便当却还没有完成的经历呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.84,0:10:28.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从某种意义上说真是厉害…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.58,0:10:39.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思 让我小睡一会儿吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.03,0:10:41.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我休息了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.59,0:10:47.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么快就睡了啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.01,0:11:28.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祐巳同学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.72,0:11:31.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么富士山会在这儿?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.93,0:11:35.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.46,0:11:37.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要给我算命签…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.16,0:11:47.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祐巳 祐巳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.30,0:11:53.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,休息站到了 去上个洗手间吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.99,0:12:01.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然想吃冰淇淋 真是长不大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.30,0:12:04.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好吃的哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.75,0:12:05.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赶快吃掉吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.22,0:12:07.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.49,0:12:10.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.25,0:12:19.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要说冰淇淋和祥子大人的共通之处
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.29,0:12:25.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就在于那既冰凉却又温柔的内心吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.77,0:12:30.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这一带是历史悠久的别墅区
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.25,0:12:36.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这儿是姐姐大人喜爱的世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.13,0:12:41.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在共度的时光里 哪怕多一个也好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.62,0:12:43.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想尽量去接触姐姐大人她喜欢的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.65,0:12:50.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.43,0:13:01.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎回来 大小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.23,0:13:04.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喜代和源助也很有精神呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.10,0:13:08.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们是负责打理别墅的泽村夫妇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.27,0:13:11.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫福泽祐巳 麻烦你们关照了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.69,0:13:14.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎您 祐巳小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.86,0:13:20.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,旅途劳累 快请进里边休息吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.29,0:13:25.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃惊了吗? 这里又旧又小
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.48,0:13:29.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪里会 很棒的房子呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.72,0:13:32.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为是小笠原家的别墅而有点不安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.94,0:13:34.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是这样的地方的话 应该没问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.07,0:13:40.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祐巳小姐家里寄给祥子小姐的大米送到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.92,0:13:42.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大…大米?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.68,0:13:43.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈真是的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.68,0:13:43.84,reference,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs26}鱼沼产越光米:越光米是日本很受欢迎的优质稻米品种 其中以新泻县鱼沼地区所产的最为闻名
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.77,0:13:47.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祐巳家真好呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.96,0:13:50.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成长在这种家庭环境下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.53,0:13:53.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才能培养出像祐巳和祐麒这样的孩子吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.83,0:13:56.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这算是在称赞我们吗…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.08,0:13:58.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喜代 在我们住的这段时间里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.80,0:14:01.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请务必用这些米来做饭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.08,0:14:03.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.34,0:14:13.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祐巳的房间是这间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.32,0:14:16.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不住在同一间房间吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.44,0:14:19.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我晚上可能会看点书
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.58,0:14:22.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起的话祐巳会因为太亮而睡不着的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.09,0:14:24.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.15,0:14:26.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去整理一下行李吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.53,0:14:37.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论如何 总算来到姐姐大人的别墅了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.21,0:14:45.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然在学校里是大家的红蔷薇大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.07,0:14:48.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这一星期里却是只属于我的姐姐大人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.23,0:14:59.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祐巳小姐 请用午餐吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.41,0:15:00.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐大人呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.18,0:15:05.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大小姐说想躺一会儿 正在楼上休息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.08,0:15:08.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会不会是哪里不舒服了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.30,0:15:10.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 每年都是如此的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.22,0:15:15.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到这儿的当天 总要休息到傍晚时分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.99,0:15:18.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.90,0:15:23.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正如喜代所言 当姐姐大人起床时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.81,0:15:25.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经是晚餐的时间了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.71,0:15:33.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我睡着的时间里 祐巳在做什么呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.68,0:15:36.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…整理行李之类的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.70,0:15:38.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有稍微躺一会儿等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.85,0:15:40.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里安安静静的很不错吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.61,0:15:42.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.35,0:15:47.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…没和姐姐大人一起稍稍有些寂寞呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.11,0:15:48.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.78,0:15:54.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 晚上来一起玩些游戏之类的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.64,0:15:55.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.93,0:15:56.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.57,0:15:58.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.30,0:16:01.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祐巳 吃饭时不要站起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.99,0:16:02.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.45,0:16:08.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不巧别墅里只有扑克牌 国际象棋和围棋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.12,0:16:11.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但和姐姐大人一起的时光非常欢乐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.80,0:16:15.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们沉浸在游戏之中直到十二点半才结束
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.60,0:16:20.70,day,NTP,0,0,0,,星期二{\fad(500,0)}{\pos(502,520)}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.18,0:16:22.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.45,0:16:24.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早安 祐巳小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.03,0:16:26.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨晚休息得好吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.95,0:16:30.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯! 这儿比起东京要凉快多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.73,0:16:32.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨晚睡得可香了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.34,0:16:33.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 好香
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.07,0:16:36.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚出炉就买回来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.43,0:16:39.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请趁热享用吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.28,0:16:42.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祐巳小姐 趁面包和煎蛋还没冷掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.49,0:16:45.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请去叫祥子小姐起床吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.14,0:16:45.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.21,0:16:59.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐大人?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.80,0:17:00.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打扰了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.36,0:17:19.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是看得出神的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.08,0:17:20.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.94,0:17:22.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐大人~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.66,0:17:27.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,起床了 已经是早上啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.04,0:17:29.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,面包和煎蛋要冷掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.64,0:17:32.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早点不吃了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.72,0:17:34.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我继续睡觉吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.71,0:17:35.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.02,0:17:39.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想要和姐姐大人一起吃早餐啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.72,0:17:40.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要掀被子了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.75,0:17:43.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请快起床
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.82,0:17:46.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.41,0:17:48.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我起床还不行吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.25,0:17:54.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祐巳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.06,0:17:55.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.59,0:17:57.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我五分钟后就出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.39,0:17:59.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.17,0:18:05.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊! 那我到下面等您了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.33,0:18:08.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是笨蛋!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.13,0:18:11.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可以呆看着姐姐大人换衣服啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.82,0:18:23.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这本是什么书?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.24,0:18:27.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暑假作业 要写读后感的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.84,0:18:30.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祐巳也趁早把暑假作业完成吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.19,0:18:33.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来的时间有很多预定的事情的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.03,0:18:36.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 今天要出门去吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.85,0:18:38.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 哪里都不去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.67,0:18:41.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但不是说过暑假后半段时间里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.59,0:18:45.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,山百合会要忙于准备学园祭的吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.50,0:18:46.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.15,0:18:48.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的作业呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.37,0:18:51.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有带过来…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.59,0:18:54.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要写读后感的书也没有带来吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.85,0:18:56.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.49,0:19:04.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么我可以帮忙的吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.86,0:19:06.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是不敢当
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.82,0:19:08.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您既然是祥子小姐的妹妹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.22,0:19:12.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就相当于小笠原家的小姐一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.19,0:19:16.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让您帮忙的话我可会被斥责的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.71,0:19:19.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,另外 您可别和我抢工作呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.65,0:19:21.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.36,0:19:34.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早知如此 就算把填字游戏带来也好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.15,0:19:37.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,松鼠…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.04,0:19:39.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.00,0:19:45.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被讨厌了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.25,0:19:47.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真无聊啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.75,0:19:51.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,盛夏之时致上问候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.39,0:19:55.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我现在正在祥子大人的别墅作客
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.72,0:19:59.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里既凉爽又很安静
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.51,0:20:04.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能将这清新的空气一同寄上实属遗憾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.94,0:20:05.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祐巳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.85,0:20:12.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只压了半天时间的叶子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.04,0:20:15.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用来当标本还不够吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.07,0:20:20.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要能维持到由乃同学和志摩子同学收到就够了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.70,0:20:21.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.01,0:20:23.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然作业没带来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.98,0:20:26.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明信片和邮票倒是准备齐全了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.41,0:20:29.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为是旅行的必备之物嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.06,0:20:33.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把这儿的住址也写上吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.84,0:20:42.99,day,NTP,0,0,0,,星期三{\fad(500,500)}{\pos(502,520)}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.41,0:20:38.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天姐姐大人也仍然在读书
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.58,0:20:42.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也从书架上借了本夏目漱石作品陪着看 不过…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.71,0:20:47.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有客人找祐巳小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.92,0:20:48.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.91,0:20:51.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帮你送忘了带的东西过来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.07,0:20:52.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.00,0:20:55.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,特地买了却忘在屋子里了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.37,0:20:59.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有这个 愉快的假期就无法开始了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.54,0:21:03.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨…别说多余的话啦!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.53,0:21:06.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祐巳 对送东西来的人怎么可以用这种态度!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.14,0:21:07.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.06,0:21:09.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祐麒同学 请进屋里来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.09,0:21:12.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就到午饭时间了 一起吃个饭吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.10,0:21:17.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不了 和学生会的朋友们约好了在大街上会合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.81,0:21:22.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家才刚到就急着要逛街去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:22.42,0:21:24.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 你们要去大街上玩吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.34,0:21:27.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还没去过吗? 要不要一起来?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:27.56,0:21:28.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.54,0:21:30.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祐巳 你去玩玩好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:30.91,0:21:33.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和祐麒一起的话我也放心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:34.03,0:21:35.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祥子同学也一起去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.09,0:21:39.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经去过了 而且不习惯这种热闹的地方…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:40.53,0:21:42.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用顾虑我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.14,0:21:43.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:44.39,0:21:46.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 就借用一下老姐了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.16,0:21:47.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祐巳 走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.62,0:21:48.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.91,0:21:54.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样不行啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:55.08,0:21:55.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么不行?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.24,0:21:58.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你脸上完全一副想去的表情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.53,0:22:01.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是写在脸上了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:01.79,0:22:04.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 你那因为顾虑祥子同学而说不去的态度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:04.89,0:22:06.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对她很失礼的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:06.90,0:22:07.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:10.87,0:22:12.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗨 小麒和祐巳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:13.75,0:22:14.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,柏木同学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:31.89,0:22:33.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多谢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:33.63,0:22:36.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是祐巳的话 我随时都乐意效劳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:36.74,0:22:37.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先告辞了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:41.29,0:22:41.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祐巳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:43.55,0:22:44.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要加油哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:44.91,0:22:45.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么意思?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:46.66,0:22:49.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么 只是有些预感
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:50.47,0:22:51.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,山雨欲来的样子…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:52.73,0:22:55.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为这里是祐巳的客场嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:56.11,0:22:57.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,客场?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:02.11,0:23:02.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回来了~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:06.17,0:23:07.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祐巳 回来了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:07.65,0:23:08.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过来这边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:08.88,0:23:09.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:20.25,0:23:24.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位 这位是我在学校里的妹妹福泽祐巳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:27.04,0:23:29.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她会在这里住到星期一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:30.08,0:23:31.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家好好相处吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:32.16,0:23:33.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请…请多关照
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:35.43,0:23:37.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是绫小路菊代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:37.99,0:23:39.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请祐巳大人多多关照
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:40.21,0:23:41.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是西园寺由佳里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:42.31,0:23:46.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能当上祥子大人的妹妹 真是羡慕您
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:46.32,0:23:50.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫京极贵惠子 希望能好好相处
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:52.59,0:23:53.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瞳子…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:54.53,0:23:56.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贵安 祐巳大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:57.44,0:23:58.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祐巳也坐下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:05.23,0:24:09.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些人回去后一定会立刻开始传播祐巳大人的传闻吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:10.69,0:24:12.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么样的传闻?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:12.66,0:24:16.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家一直都憧憬着祥子大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:17.01,0:24:20.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对于后来居上抢走妹妹宝座的祐巳大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:20.68,0:24:22.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,显然不会去传播什么好听的话了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:23.19,0:24:26.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊 就是说又增加了三个瞳子呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:26.75,0:24:29.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呵呵 是不是有点可怕?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:29.75,0:24:30.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贵安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:30.82,0:24:31.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贵安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:33.82,0:24:35.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,镇上好玩吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:35.47,0:24:36.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:36.68,0:24:37.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:37.91,0:24:40.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是跟姐姐大人在一起更好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:50.42,0:24:54.23,day,NTP,0,0,0,,星期四{\fad(500,500)}{\pos(502,520)}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:58.04,0:25:01.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赤松 落叶松 桂树 枫树
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:01.89,0:25:03.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等到秋天就会是一片红叶的景致了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:08.31,0:25:10.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听见了吗? 这是琉璃鸟的叫声哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:11.12,0:25:12.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您知道的真多呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:14.26,0:25:16.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小心 那里有断落的树枝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:26.75,0:25:28.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这雾也是我喜欢的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:28.82,0:25:30.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望让你也看看这片景象
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:35.58,0:25:37.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐大人所喜爱的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:37.72,0:25:40.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是自家的别墅和周围的大自然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:45.72,0:25:46.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里对姐姐大人来说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:47.41,0:25:50.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是如同孩提时代的房间一样能平静心神的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:52.01,0:25:54.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如此特别的一个只属于自己的重要空间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:55.30,0:25:57.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而姐姐大人却邀请我进入了这个地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:00.94,0:26:01.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐大人~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:04.50,0:26:07.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了? 在雾里觉得害怕吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:11.91,0:26:14.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样就不要紧了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:14.75,0:26:18.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喜欢恶作剧的妖精只会找上落单的人的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:29.01,0:26:32.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菊代 作业应该自己完成哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:33.37,0:26:34.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:35.42,0:26:39.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我每年都是期待着能让祥子姐姐辅导功课
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:40.27,0:26:42.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才到别墅来的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:43.65,0:26:46.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是说今年因为有了祐巳大人在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:46.49,0:26:49.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菊代的事就无关紧要了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:50.74,0:26:52.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和祐巳无关的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:53.60,0:26:54.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祐巳大人太狡猾了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:55.83,0:26:58.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从早到晚都独占着祥子姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:59.33,0:27:03.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,却连一点点的时间也不愿分给我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:03.75,0:27:04.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,实在是贪得无厌!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:06.52,0:27:10.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为祐巳大人的缘故 祥子姐姐都变了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:14.89,0:27:16.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菊代 别哭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:19.06,0:27:21.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去楼上看书了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:25.31,0:27:27.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祐巳 对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:27.24,0:27:27.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:36.97,0:27:39.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是待在喜欢的人身边而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:39.85,0:27:42.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,却使得别的什么人感到悲伤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:45.36,0:27:49.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 喜欢一个人是很重要的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:50.17,0:27:51.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要加油啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:52.73,0:27:55.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 一波未平一波又起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:55.86,0:27:56.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到了下午的时候…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:59.92,0:28:03.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,母亲说想见见祥子姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:04.05,0:28:05.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本该过来拜访的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:06.55,0:28:07.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不巧却有点感冒…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:08.32,0:28:11.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 京极伯母她感冒了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:12.18,0:28:14.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去探望一下如何?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:14.91,0:28:16.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祐巳 你呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:16.81,0:28:21.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,留守看家 顺便借用这里的书 写读后感的草稿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:22.07,0:28:24.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀 祐巳大人也可以一起来嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:25.05,0:28:26.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,陌生人前去打扰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:26.95,0:28:30.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怕会影响到贵惠子小姐母亲的身体状况
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:31.18,0:28:33.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊…真是遗憾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:39.42,0:28:40.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祐巳小姐 说几句话行吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:40.87,0:28:41.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:46.13,0:28:48.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请您小心那几位小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:50.41,0:28:55.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,京极小姐向我打听了很多祐巳小姐的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:55.55,0:28:56.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的事情?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:57.16,0:29:01.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我原以为她是为了更亲近祐巳小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:02.34,0:29:07.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以说了许多祐巳小姐过来之后的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:08.08,0:29:12.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是对不起 我应该多留个心眼才对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:13.01,0:29:16.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系啦 又没什么不可告人的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:17.39,0:29:19.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 您说得不错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:20.21,0:29:28.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是那些小姐们很讲究门第和排场之类的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:28.19,0:29:30.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因此有些担心…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:31.95,0:29:33.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽说叫我小心…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:33.94,0:29:36.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可我该小心什么 又该如何去注意呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:50.01,0:29:51.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发生什么事情了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:51.57,0:29:52.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么好说的!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:53.81,0:29:54.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我到了那边一看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:54.80,0:29:58.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,京极家一伙人正聚在花园里开派对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:59.55,0:30:01.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那贵惠子小姐的母亲呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:01.94,0:30:03.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,活蹦乱跳着呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:03.72,0:30:06.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,病人在大白天里就灌着香槟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:06.20,0:30:08.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还把堆成山的烤肉往嘴里塞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:08.74,0:30:09.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这到底是怎么回事?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:11.25,0:30:14.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事…问我这个我也…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:17.21,0:30:20.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 不该对祐巳发脾气的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:20.67,0:30:21.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:21.52,0:30:23.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算了 我们回东京去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:24.21,0:30:25.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发生什么事了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:26.83,0:30:29.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么 只是觉得厌烦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:30.48,0:30:33.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,厌烦了和一些人像闹剧般的交际来往
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:36.04,0:30:40.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只不过想和祐巳一起悠闲地度过 可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:40.57,0:30:42.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么就不能放过我们呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:43.46,0:30:46.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有时候 小笠原这个姓氏让我觉得沉重
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:47.31,0:30:49.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我深爱着父母和祖父
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:49.66,0:30:55.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也很感谢他们花费了不寻常的精力和财力将我养育至今
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:56.41,0:30:59.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我偶尔却会梦想着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:00.99,0:31:03.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在一个如这别墅般大小的家里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:03.59,0:31:06.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一家四口在一起生活该有多好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:07.63,0:31:11.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 小时候一家人趁着盂兰盆节假期
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:11.41,0:31:14.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起到这里度过时我总是非常开心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:15.38,0:31:18.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父亲和祖父也只有住在这里的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:19.23,0:31:21.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才不会去找外头的女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:36.53,0:31:39.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因此姐姐大人才会喜欢这个地方啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:41.92,0:31:43.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然如此 就别说要回去之类的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:44.10,0:31:45.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尽量在这里多待些时候吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:46.96,0:31:49.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这里的话 我没有办法保护你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:49.97,0:31:50.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:50.82,0:31:53.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,京极家里 在传着你的话题呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:54.62,0:31:56.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我被说了些什么了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:56.39,0:31:57.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愚蠢透顶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:57.57,0:32:01.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算莉莉安瓦版也不会去登这么无聊的话题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:02.22,0:32:05.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 有多么的无聊 请说给我听听看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:07.09,0:32:08.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大米的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:08.39,0:32:09.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:09.80,0:32:10.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是大米的那件事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:11.15,0:32:12.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经够了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:12.62,0:32:15.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种话题根本不值得你听
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:17.16,0:32:17.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:18.44,0:32:21.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我的事让姐姐大人蒙羞了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:22.44,0:32:23.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是这样的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:24.46,0:32:27.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我从没有觉得你让我蒙羞过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:28.00,0:32:28.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不明白吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:29.36,0:32:31.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想让你受到伤害啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:32.07,0:32:35.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只因为你是我的妹妹 就得受这样的委屈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:35.69,0:32:37.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我最不想看到的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:39.34,0:32:40.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐大人在生气着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:41.95,0:32:47.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可我却能以如此平静的心情看着姐姐大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:48.02,0:32:49.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是不可思议
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:50.39,0:32:55.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本希望你能一直觉得和我在一起是件开心的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:55.71,0:32:56.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很开心哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:57.86,0:32:58.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,骗人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:59.19,0:33:00.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:01.67,0:33:05.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是痛苦和悲伤 我也一样乐在其中啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:09.86,0:33:13.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和姐姐大人在一起的事实本身就是我的幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:14.00,0:33:16.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么姐姐大人还不能明白呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:17.94,0:33:18.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祐巳…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:19.17,0:33:23.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以如果姐姐大人想回去的话我当然跟随
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:24.43,0:33:28.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果决心留下的话我也会陪伴到底的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:30.57,0:33:31.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:31.82,0:33:36.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是这样想的话 就按原计划待到星期一吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:37.14,0:33:40.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我这个人其实最讨厌逃避了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:40.97,0:33:42.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这才是我的姐姐大人嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:44.40,0:33:45.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祐巳…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:46.74,0:33:50.24,day,NTP,0,0,0,,星期五{\fad(500,500)}{\pos(502,520)}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:51.05,0:33:52.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也有寄给你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:53.28,0:33:54.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也有?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:55.30,0:33:56.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（福泽祐巳小姐）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:56.54,0:33:58.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（星期六傍晚六时开始在别墅举行派对）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:58.87,0:33:59.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（请务必赏光 恭候您的光临）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:59.97,0:34:01.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（西园寺由佳里）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:02.24,0:34:02.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,派对…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:07.80,0:34:10.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天是绫小路小姐和京极小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:10.83,0:34:12.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来明天是西园寺小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:13.88,0:34:16.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来还有一难等在前头啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:22.74,0:34:25.45,day,NTP,0,0,0,,星期六{\fad(500,0)}{\pos(502,520)}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:29.29,0:34:31.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家 怎么会…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:33.65,0:34:37.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 是读了我的明信片才特地赶过来的吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:38.08,0:34:41.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为祐巳同学会用那么郑重的文笔写了明信片寄来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:42.17,0:34:45.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难免让人觉得你不是无聊 就是发生什么事了嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:46.42,0:34:48.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后打电话给志摩子同学商量后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:48.62,0:34:51.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就觉得既然担心的话 不如过来看看好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:52.06,0:34:54.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为你把这里的详细地址也写上了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:54.43,0:34:57.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,于是猜测这也许是希望我们来的暗示呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:57.91,0:35:00.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 那个是姐姐大人写的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:00.94,0:35:03.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 看来我好像太主观臆断了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:04.72,0:35:08.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 也许是红蔷薇大人希望大家能来呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:09.49,0:35:10.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐大人她?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:13.95,0:35:16.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把这儿的住址也写上吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:17.57,0:35:20.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐大人为了我把大家叫来这里…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:21.72,0:35:24.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 祥子现在去哪了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:24.75,0:35:26.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到松平家的别墅去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:27.28,0:35:29.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去问候瞳子的爷爷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:30.05,0:35:32.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来我们是来对了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:33.54,0:35:36.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祐巳同学正为什么事而烦恼吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:37.07,0:35:39.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦~ 又表现在脸上了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:42.77,0:35:43.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然没理由去啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:44.69,0:35:46.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也认为不去比较好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:47.10,0:35:47.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:49.44,0:35:51.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是幼稚的做法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:51.64,0:35:53.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像是小学生欺负别人似的行为
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:54.64,0:35:56.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祥子她怎么说?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:56.73,0:35:58.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎还犹豫不决
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:58.65,0:36:00.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此 我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:01.16,0:36:02.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道什么了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:03.87,0:36:05.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祥子现在正在动摇着呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:06.54,0:36:09.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对于别人的挑衅 基本上她都会挺身相对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:09.77,0:36:15.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是 看不清对手是谁或不清楚对方想法的情况下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:16.04,0:36:18.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她就会变得非常胆怯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:19.13,0:36:20.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我好像有一点明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:21.49,0:36:24.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果只有自己一个的话 她大概是会去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:24.96,0:36:27.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但这次祐巳大人也一起被邀请了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:28.16,0:36:29.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是原因了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:29.42,0:36:30.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对现在的祥子来说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:30.73,0:36:33.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起自己 她更担心祐巳被为难
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:33.95,0:36:35.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以她才会犹豫不决
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:36.38,0:36:37.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祐巳同学的想法是怎样的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:38.93,0:36:44.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得…无论自己怎么选择都不是正确的答案
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:45.07,0:36:46.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是正确的答案?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:46.80,0:36:50.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去参加派对的话 我想一定会有不愉快的事发生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:50.70,0:36:56.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但如果不去 以后迟早会因为逃避而付出成倍的代价
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:56.70,0:37:01.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管怎样 我决定遵从祥子大人的选择去做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:01.64,0:37:03.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是可能会去的意思了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:03.67,0:37:04.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:04.59,0:37:05.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真傻啊 祐巳同学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:06.19,0:37:09.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪有人明知道是陷阱还自己往里面跳啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:09.67,0:37:12.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和我们一起搭傍晚的新干线回去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:13.81,0:37:15.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是那些大小姐们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:15.77,0:37:18.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不至于会追上来找麻烦的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:18.96,0:37:21.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢 但我是不会回去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:22.27,0:37:25.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要回去也是和姐姐大人一起回 我已经决定了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:26.55,0:37:30.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都来了啊 真是太高兴了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:31.24,0:37:33.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贵安 红蔷薇大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:33.67,0:37:37.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们看到明信片上的地址 就厚着脸皮不请自来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:38.33,0:37:41.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这一带对外来者而言简直就是个迷宫呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:42.27,0:37:46.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是不知道门牌号码的话 也许就找不到这里了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:46.24,0:37:49.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吧 所以这儿的地址是不轻易告诉别人的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:50.63,0:37:52.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里可是祥子的秘密基地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:52.87,0:37:54.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 秘密基地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:56.18,0:37:58.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暑假过得开心吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:58.47,0:37:59.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:59.43,0:38:03.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和乃梨子到各处参观能当天往返的佛像展和教堂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:04.42,0:38:08.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来这里的途中 还去参拜了石制的观音菩萨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:08.86,0:38:10.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊 那你们这对呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:11.42,0:38:12.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,登富士山感觉如何?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:13.33,0:38:14.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真不怎么样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:14.72,0:38:16.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了在日出前到达山顶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:16.70,0:38:19.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中途在小木屋里小睡了一阵子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:19.54,0:38:23.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但那里睡觉的人太多 挤得根本动弹不得
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:24.25,0:38:26.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,旁边居然还睡了一个超胖的阿姨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:26.82,0:38:29.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又是打鼾又是磨牙 真是要命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:30.05,0:38:30.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日出呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:31.60,0:38:33.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大饱眼福了一番
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:33.64,0:38:35.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看吧 脚都被鞋子磨破了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:36.18,0:38:39.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由乃这狡猾的家伙 半路上换成骑马了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:39.42,0:38:41.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小令 说了这个要保密的了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:43.51,0:38:44.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小令!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:49.02,0:38:50.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住一晚再走多好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:51.49,0:38:53.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干脆祥子也一起回去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:57.85,0:38:59.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 学校里再见了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:59.76,0:39:01.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 回头见了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:13.14,0:39:13.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祐巳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:14.11,0:39:14.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:15.34,0:39:16.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的没关系吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:16.66,0:39:17.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:18.73,0:39:21.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我陪您一起去参加西园寺小姐的派对吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:29.52,0:39:30.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作好心理准备了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:31.56,0:39:33.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 没问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:34.07,0:39:36.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算不幸受到了重大的打击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:36.95,0:39:40.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要有姐姐大人温柔的笑容 我就能立刻振作起来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:43.70,0:39:47.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎光临 祥子姐姐 祐巳小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:48.07,0:39:49.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多谢你能邀请我们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:49.60,0:39:50.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来 里面请
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:59.66,0:40:03.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位 小笠原家的祥子姐姐到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:04.21,0:40:08.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有 大家久等的福泽祐巳小姐也一起来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:14.92,0:40:16.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去拿点喝的来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:17.05,0:40:17.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:20.53,0:40:23.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是传说的越光米公主哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:25.70,0:40:26.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,越光米…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:27.26,0:40:31.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我之前邀请她来我家的别墅 居然被拒绝了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:34.70,0:40:36.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祐巳大人 你该不会是受虐狂吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:38.09,0:40:38.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瞳子…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:39.81,0:40:42.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都那样忠告过你了 会发生什么事我可不管了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:43.45,0:40:45.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不如趁现在赶快回去如何?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:47.09,0:40:49.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们姐妹俩真是有胆量呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:49.93,0:40:50.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,柏木同学…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:51.38,0:40:55.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明知是鸿门宴 却还是来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:56.62,0:41:00.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 为什么非要刁难我不可呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:01.33,0:41:04.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为她们对小笠原家抱有自卑情结啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:04.31,0:41:05.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小笠原家?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:05.85,0:41:08.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 那个家族是历史悠久的名门
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:08.66,0:41:09.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相比之下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:10.54,0:41:12.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这几位小姐家里却没什么家世可言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:13.68,0:41:16.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对于这些整天把家世挂在嘴边的人来说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:16.72,0:41:18.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,面对小笠原家自然会感到自卑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:19.12,0:41:22.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我并不是小笠原家的人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:24.12,0:41:25.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然身为小祥的妹妹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:26.19,0:41:28.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就如同是小笠原家的小姐一样了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:29.96,0:41:31.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉让你久等了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:31.86,0:41:34.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才遇上了以前的书法老师…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:35.49,0:41:36.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们在聊些什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:36.65,0:41:37.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:49.01,0:41:50.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开始了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:50.41,0:41:51.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那位是…?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:51.63,0:41:53.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,西园寺家的老夫人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:54.19,0:41:57.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天是她八十八岁寿辰的庆生派对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:58.44,0:42:02.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然是曾祖母的生日 我一点也不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:05.51,0:42:06.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祝贺您
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:07.24,0:42:09.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祝贺您
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:11.03,0:42:15.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有被告知派对主题的 只有我们而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:17.34,0:42:20.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,曾祖母 祝您生日快乐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:28.36,0:42:29.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么接下来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:30.35,0:42:35.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由大家为曾祖母献上她最喜爱的音乐作为礼物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:36.17,0:42:37.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先由我开始吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:02.15,0:43:03.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那位老夫人难道…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:04.16,0:43:05.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生病了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:05.66,0:43:07.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 她这是在生气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:08.78,0:43:11.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为孩子们擅自改建了这幢别墅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:12.42,0:43:14.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她很生气并对家人们都不理不睬了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:51.22,0:43:52.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 祐巳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:52.62,0:43:53.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在乐器方面如何?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:53.91,0:43:56.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小时候学过一点钢琴…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:56.72,0:43:58.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但现在已经不会弹了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:00.92,0:44:01.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道说!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:10.91,0:44:11.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祐巳小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:12.55,0:44:16.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以为曾祖母演奏一曲吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:16.57,0:44:19.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么都行 只要说出你擅长的乐器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:19.93,0:44:21.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一般的乐器我们家里都有准备的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:23.89,0:44:24.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:32.83,0:44:33.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祐巳…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:43.88,0:44:44.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:46.57,0:44:47.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祐巳!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:48.99,0:44:51.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祐巳 已经够了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:54.52,0:44:55.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要紧的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:56.07,0:44:56.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祐巳…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:10.17,0:45:13.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恕我不才 对乐器没有什么心得
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:13.95,0:45:18.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但为了祝贺您的生日 请允许我为曾祖母…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:18.81,0:45:19.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,献上一曲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:23.64,0:45:31.03,ed_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}マリア様のこころ それは青空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:31.56,0:45:39.06,ed_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}私たちを包む 広い青空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:39.55,0:45:47.22,ed_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}マリア様のこころ それは樫の木
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:47.60,0:45:54.99,ed_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}私たちを守る 強い樫の木
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:59.35,0:46:06.50,ed_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}マリア様のこころ それは鶯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:07.01,0:46:14.34,ed_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}私たちと歌う 森の鶯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:14.85,0:46:22.11,ed_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}マリア様のこころ それは山百合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:22.59,0:46:29.77,ed_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}私たちも欲しい 白い山百合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:30.38,0:46:37.70,ed_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}マリア様のこころ それはサファイア
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:38.18,0:46:46.28,ed_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}私たちを飾る 光るサファイア
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:23.64,0:45:31.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,圣母玛莉亚之心 是那片蓝天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:31.56,0:45:39.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,包容着我们的 广阔的蓝天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:39.55,0:45:47.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,圣母玛莉亚之心 是那棵橡树
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:47.60,0:45:54.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,守护着我们的 坚强的橡树
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:59.35,0:46:06.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,圣母玛莉亚之心 是那只黄莺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:07.01,0:46:14.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与我们齐唱的 林中的黄莺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:14.85,0:46:22.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,圣母玛莉亚之心 是那山百合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:22.59,0:46:29.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们所向往的 白色山百合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:30.38,0:46:37.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,圣母玛莉亚之心 是那蓝宝石
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:38.18,0:46:46.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,装饰着我们的 闪耀蓝宝石
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:15.58,0:47:18.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你美妙的歌声
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:19.52,0:47:21.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我想起了过去的时光呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:24.46,0:47:25.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,献给您
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:33.27,0:47:35.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你唱的是「圣母玛莉亚之心」吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:35.79,0:47:36.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:38.14,0:47:41.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明年也请再过来玩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:42.11,0:47:43.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天使小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:53.21,0:47:55.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天就是住在这别墅的最后一天了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:56.33,0:47:57.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就按祐巳所喜欢的去度过吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:58.46,0:47:59.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想做些什么呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:00.07,0:48:02.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想无所事事地过一天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:03.03,0:48:03.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无所事事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:04.68,0:48:06.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想和姐姐大人一起睡午觉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:07.11,0:48:07.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:08.48,0:48:13.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想明天一整天既不见客也不读书
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:13.67,0:48:15.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只在阳台上铺上垫子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:15.74,0:48:18.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和姐姐大人单独两个人懒洋洋地度过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:19.28,0:48:21.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 听起来真是不错呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:21.87,0:48:22.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赞成了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:23.40,0:48:24.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然喽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:29.63,0:48:31.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐大人 怎么了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:32.46,0:48:36.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才呀 我吓得心脏都要跳出来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:37.42,0:48:40.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才…是指我要唱歌的时候吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:41.08,0:48:41.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:42.64,0:48:45.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:47.51,0:48:49.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底什么那么好笑的啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:50.14,0:48:51.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为…那时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:52.13,0:48:55.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还担心你该不会是想要跳安来节舞蹈呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:52.13,0:48:55.20,reference,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs26}安来节:源于日本岛根县安来地区的民谣艺术 根据农民在田中用篓子捞泥鳅的滑稽样子\N创作出相应音乐与舞蹈 十分幽默 祐巳曾在前蔷薇大人们的送别会上表演过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:55.94,0:48:56.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安来节?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:59.84,0:49:01.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为是你的话也说不定会跳的嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:05.24,0:49:08.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讨厌~ 姐姐大人真是的~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:10.04,0:49:12.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了吧 笑够了没有啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:12.95,0:49:14.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐大人~~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:17.60,0:51:19.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就快到花寺学院的学园祭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:19.64,0:51:22.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每年山百合会都会按惯例去帮忙的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:22.57,0:51:26.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这之前 弟弟祐麒提出希望双方能先碰个面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:26.37,0:51:27.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,问题出在那一位身上吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:27.93,0:51:30.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有厌男症的祥子大人到底会不会答应呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:30.77,0:51:32.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就得靠祐巳同学想想办法了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:32.58,0:51:33.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 就命名为
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:33.80,0:51:36.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为避免突然被丢进男子学校受到严重刺激
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:36.50,0:51:39.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而用逐渐适应的办法来克服厌男症的大作战
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:39.60,0:51:40.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不觉得太长了点吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:40.91,0:51:42.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那…「克服厌男症」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:40.91,0:51:44.29,reference,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs26}注:克服厌男症（男嫌い克服  Otokogirai Kokufuku）的日语发音首字母是O和K
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:42.75,0:51:44.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就简称为「OK大作战」吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:44.44,0:51:45.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能顺利地…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:45.20,0:51:46.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,进行就好了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:42.12,0:51:47.01,next,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(800,0)}{\pos(675,420)}简称OK大作战（暂）
